  "displayTitle": "<span class=\"mw-page-title-main\">Frozen Banana Daiquiri</span>",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-content-ltr mw-parser-output\"><p><i>Exclusive to:</i> <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Don%27t_Starve_Together\" title=\"Don&#x27;t Starve Together\"><img alt=\"Don&#x27;t Starve Together icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Don%27t_Starve_Together_icon.png/32px-Don%27t_Starve_Together_icon.png?3bc208\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\"></a><br>\n</p>\n\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n\n<p><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Frozen Banana Daiquiri</a> is a <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\">Crock Pot</a> recipe exclusive to <i><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Don%27t_Starve_Together\" title=\"Don&#x27;t Starve Together\">Don&#x27;t Starve Together</a></i> introduced in the <i><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/An_Eye_for_An_Eye\" title=\"An Eye for An Eye\">An Eye for An Eye</a></i> update. It is made from 1 <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Cave_Banana\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Cave Banana\">Banana</a>, 1 <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Ice\" title=\"Ice\">Ice</a>, and 2 filler.\n</p><p>Using <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Twigs\" title=\"Twigs\">Twigs</a> as filler will result in a <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Banana_Pop\" title=\"Banana Pop\">Banana Pop</a>. Adding any additional Bananas may result in <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Banana_Shake\" title=\"Banana Shake\">Banana Shake</a>. Adding more than 1 <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Durian\" title=\"Durian\">Durian</a> will result in <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Monster_Lasagna\" title=\"Monster Lasagna\">Monster Lasagna</a>. Although <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Ice_Bream\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Ice Bream\">Ice Bream</a> may be considered ice, using it in a recipe will result in a meat product other than Frozen Banana Daiquiri.\n</p><p>Frozen Banana Daiquiri is a Goodies type dish, meaning that Wigfrid can eat but Beefalo will not eat this recipe, though they eat Banana Pops.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recipe\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Cookbook\" title=\"Cookbook\"><img alt=\"Cookbook.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Cookbook.png/32px-Cookbook.png?a6d040\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a>Recipe</span></h2>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Cave_Bananas\" title=\"Cave Bananas\"><img alt=\"Bananas.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Bananas.png?6e67ce\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Ice\" title=\"Ice\"><img alt=\"Ice.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Ice.png?8c6842\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Filler\" title=\"Filler\"><img alt=\"Filler.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Filler.png?b5d099\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Filler\" title=\"Filler\"><img alt=\"Filler.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Filler.png?b5d099\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\"><img alt=\"Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Crock_Pot.png/42px-Crock_Pot.png?8263f1\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Frozen_Banana_Daiquiri\" title=\"Frozen Banana Daiquiri\"><img alt=\"Frozen Banana Daiquiri.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Frozen_Banana_Daiquiri.png?9fbec9\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td>Fillers cannot be <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Meats\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Meats\">Meats</a> or <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Fishes\" title=\"Fishes\">Fishes</a>.</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Examples\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\"><img alt=\"Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Crock_Pot.png/32px-Crock_Pot.png?8263f1\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a>Examples</span></h2>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Cave_Banana\" title=\"Cave Banana\"><img alt=\"Banana.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Banana.png?ba11e2\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Ice\" title=\"Ice\"><img alt=\"Ice.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Ice.png?8c6842\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Ice\" title=\"Ice\"><img alt=\"Ice.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Ice.png?8c6842\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Ice\" title=\"Ice\"><img alt=\"Ice.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Ice.png?8c6842\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\"><img alt=\"Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Crock_Pot.png/42px-Crock_Pot.png?8263f1\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Frozen_Banana_Daiquiri\" title=\"Frozen Banana Daiquiri\"><img alt=\"Frozen Banana Daiquiri.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Frozen_Banana_Daiquiri.png?9fbec9\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Cave_Banana\" title=\"Cave Banana\"><img alt=\"Banana.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Banana.png?ba11e2\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Ice\" title=\"Ice\"><img alt=\"Ice.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Ice.png?8c6842\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Ripe_Stone_Fruit\" title=\"Ripe Stone Fruit\"><img alt=\"Ripe Stone Fruit.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Ripe_Stone_Fruit.png?4eade1\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Ripe_Stone_Fruit\" title=\"Ripe Stone Fruit\"><img alt=\"Ripe Stone Fruit.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Ripe_Stone_Fruit.png?4eade1\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\"><img alt=\"Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Crock_Pot.png/42px-Crock_Pot.png?8263f1\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Frozen_Banana_Daiquiri\" title=\"Frozen Banana Daiquiri\"><img alt=\"Frozen Banana Daiquiri.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Frozen_Banana_Daiquiri.png?9fbec9\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Cooked_Cave_Banana\" title=\"Cooked Cave Banana\"><img alt=\"Cooked Banana.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Cooked_Banana.png?1a13f0\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Ice\" title=\"Ice\"><img alt=\"Ice.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Ice.png?8c6842\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Honey\" title=\"Honey\"><img alt=\"Honey.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Honey.png?d057e9\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Honey\" title=\"Honey\"><img alt=\"Honey.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Honey.png?d057e9\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\"><img alt=\"Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Crock_Pot.png/42px-Crock_Pot.png?8263f1\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Frozen_Banana_Daiquiri\" title=\"Frozen Banana Daiquiri\"><img alt=\"Frozen Banana Daiquiri.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Frozen_Banana_Daiquiri.png?9fbec9\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Cooked_Cave_Banana\" title=\"Cooked Cave Banana\"><img alt=\"Cooked Banana.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Cooked_Banana.png?1a13f0\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Ice\" title=\"Ice\"><img alt=\"Ice.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Ice.png?8c6842\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Nightmare_Fuel\" title=\"Nightmare Fuel\"><img alt=\"Nightmare Fuel.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Nightmare_Fuel.png?9ed7c9\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Nightmare_Fuel\" title=\"Nightmare Fuel\"><img alt=\"Nightmare Fuel.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Nightmare_Fuel.png?9ed7c9\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\"><img alt=\"Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Crock_Pot.png/42px-Crock_Pot.png?8263f1\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Frozen_Banana_Daiquiri\" title=\"Frozen Banana Daiquiri\"><img alt=\"Frozen Banana Daiquiri.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Frozen_Banana_Daiquiri.png?9fbec9\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<div></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Trivia\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Placeholder\" title=\"Placeholder\"><img alt=\"Placeholder.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Placeholder.png/32px-Placeholder.png?210282\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a>Trivia</span></h2>\n<ul><li>The <a href=\"https://terraria.wiki.gg/wiki/Frozen_Banana_Daiquiri\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"wgg:terraria:Frozen Banana Daiquiri\">Frozen Banana Daiquiri</a> is an item in <i>Terraria</i>.\n<ul><li>Wilson&#x27;s quote &quot;Yellow and mellow!&quot; is a reference to its tooltip in <i>Terraria</i>.</li></ul></li>\n<li>A <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Daiquiri\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"wikipedia:Daiquiri\">Daiquiri</a> is a cocktail made from rum, citrus juice (often lime), and a sweetener. Frozen variations, including a banana daiquiri, are also common.</li></ul>\n<div class=\"tabber tabber--init\"><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"By_Type-0-label\" href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Frozen_Banana_Daiquiri#By_Type-0\">By Type</a><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"By_Crock_Pot_Value-0-label\" href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Frozen_Banana_Daiquiri#By_Crock_Pot_Value-0\">By Crock Pot Value</a><section class=\"tabber__section\"><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p></section></div>\n\n\n\n\n</div>",
