  "plainText": "Exclusive to:\nFrozen Banana Daiquiri\nFood Info\n18.75\n30\n15\nGoodies\nObject Info\nPerk\nLowers temperature by 15 degrees over 15 seconds\n15 days\nCan be Burned\n40\nCooking Info\nx1 x1.0 x2\n20 seconds\n2\nMiscellaneous\n\"frozenbananadaiquiri\"\n“Yellow and mellow!”\n–Wilson\n“Ew, it's cold.”\n–Willow\n“Cold and tasty! ANOTHER!”\n–Wolfgang\n“This won't be of help to my cold, cold heart.”\n–Wendy\n“POTASSIUM.”\n–WX-78\n“This would pair nicely with a short book.”\n–Wickerbottom\n“Nothin' like kicking back with a cold one, eh?”\n–Woodie\n“There are better beverages to make.”\n–Maxwell\n“Mönkey drink.”\n–Wigfrid\n“We can pretend it's a milkshake!”\n–Webber\n“There's no better refreshment!”\n–Warly\n“Cold friend water.”\n–Wormwood\n“Perfect after a long day of work.”\n–Winona\n“Don't the mortals like to innovate? Hyuyu.”\n–Wortox\n“Cold fruit tastes yummy, florp!”\n–Wurt\n“Don't drink it too fast or you'll get a headache.”\n–Walter\n“I'll be done with it in no time.”\n–Wanda\nFrozen Banana Daiquiri is a Crock Pot recipe exclusive to Don't Starve Together introduced in the An Eye for An Eye update. It is made from 1 Banana, 1 Ice, and 2 filler.\nUsing Twigs as filler will result in a Banana Pop. Adding any additional Bananas may result in Banana Shake. Adding more than 1 Durian will result in Monster Lasagna. Although Ice Bream may be considered ice, using it in a recipe will result in a meat product other than Frozen Banana Daiquiri.\nFrozen Banana Daiquiri is a Goodies type dish, meaning that Wigfrid can eat but Beefalo will not eat this recipe, though they eat Banana Pops.\nRecipe[edit | edit source]\nFillers cannot be Meats or Fishes.\nExamples[edit | edit source]\nTrivia[edit | edit source]\nThe Frozen Banana Daiquiri is an item in Terraria.\nWilson's quote \"Yellow and mellow!\" is a reference to its tooltip in Terraria.\nA Daiquiri is a cocktail made from rum, citrus juice (often lime), and a sweetener. Frozen variations, including a banana daiquiri, are also common.\nBy TypeBy Crock Pot Value\nView or edit this template\nFood and Edible Items (by Food Type)\nVeggie\nSeeds\nMeat\nGoodies\nGeneric\nHorrible\nRoughage\nElementals\nBurnt\nRaw\nGears\nGold Dust\nBerry\nWood\nNitre\nLunar Shards\nView or edit this template\nFood and Edible Items (by Food Value)\nMeats\nFishes\nVegetables\nFruits\nMonster Food\nEggs\nDairy\nSweetener\nFrozen\nInedibles\nMagic\nFat\nSeed\nJellyfish\nBone\nFilter\nAntihistamine\nDecoration\nBug\nNo Value Food",
