  "summaryViHtml": "<h2>Tóm tắt</h2><p>Frozen Banana Daiquiri là công thức Nồi Hầm độc quyền của Don&#x27;t Starve Together được giới thiệu trong bản cập nhật An Eye for An Eye. Nó được làm từ 1 Chuối, 1 Đá và 2 chất độn.</p>",
  "title": "Frozen Banana Daiquiri",
  "wikitext": "{{Exclusivity|Don't Starve Together}}\n{{Object Infobox\n|canBeBurned=1\n|foodType =[[Goodies]] [[File:Goodies.png|32px|link=Goodies]]\n|foodRecipe = {{Pic|32px|Cave Bananas}}x1 {{Pic|32px|Ices}}x1.0 {{Pic|32px|Filler}}x2\n|image = Frozen Banana Daiquiri Dropped.png\n|icon = Frozen Banana Daiquiri.png\n|hpRestored = 30\n|hungerRestored = 18.75\n|sanityRestored = 15\n|cooktime = 20 seconds\n|spoil = 15 days\n|priority = 2\n|perk = Lowers temperature by 15 degrees over 15 seconds\n|stack = 40\n|spawnCode = \"frozenbananadaiquiri\"}}\n{{Quotes\n|wilson = Yellow and mellow!\n|willow = Ew, it's cold.\n|wolfgang = Cold and tasty! ANOTHER!\n|wendy = This won't be of help to my cold, cold heart.\n|wx78 = POTASSIUM.\n|wickerbottom = This would pair nicely with a short book.\n|woodie = Nothin' like kicking back with a cold one, eh?\n|maxwell = There are better beverages to make.\n|wigfrid = Mönkey drink.\n|webber = We can pretend it's a milkshake!\n|winona = Perfect after a long day of work.\n|warly = There's no better refreshment!\n|wormwood = Cold friend water.\n|wortox = Don't the mortals like to innovate? Hyuyu.\n|wurt = Cold fruit tastes yummy, florp!\n|walter = Don't drink it too fast or you'll get a headache.\n|wanda = I'll be done with it in no time.}}\n\n[[Frozen Banana Daiquiri]] is a [[Crock Pot]] recipe exclusive to ''[[Don't Starve Together]]'' introduced in the ''[[An Eye for An Eye]]'' update. It is made from 1 [[Cave Banana|Banana]], 1 [[Ice]], and 2 filler.\n\nUsing [[Twigs]] as filler will result in a [[Banana Pop]]. Adding any additional Bananas may result in [[Banana Shake]]. Adding more than 1 [[Durian]] will result in [[Monster Lasagna]]. Although [[Ice Bream]] may be considered ice, using it in a recipe will result in a meat product other than Frozen Banana Daiquiri.\n\nFrozen Banana Daiquiri is a Goodies type dish, meaning that Wigfrid can eat but Beefalo will not eat this recipe, though they eat Banana Pops.\n__NOTOC__\n== {{Pic|32|Cookbook}}Recipe ==\n{{Recipe\n|item1=Cave Bananas\n|item2=Ice\n|item3=Filler\n|item4=Filler\n|result=Frozen Banana Daiquiri\n|tool=Crock Pot\n|note = Fillers cannot be [[Meats]] or [[Fishes]].\n}}\n\n== {{Pic32|Crock Pot}}Examples ==\n{{Recipe|item1=Cave Banana|item2=Ice|item3=Ice|item4=Ice|tool=Crock Pot|result=Frozen Banana Daiquiri|note=}}\n{{Recipe|item1=Cave Banana|item2=Ice|item3=Ripe Stone Fruit|item4=Ripe Stone Fruit|tool=Crock Pot|result=Frozen Banana Daiquiri}}\n{{Recipe|item1=Cooked Cave Banana|item2=Ice|item3=Honey|item4=Honey|tool=Crock Pot|result=Frozen Banana Daiquiri}}\n{{Recipe|item1=Cooked Cave Banana|item2=Ice|item3=Nightmare Fuel|item4=Nightmare Fuel|tool=Crock Pot|result=Frozen Banana Daiquiri}}\n{{clear}}\n\n== {{Pic|32|Placeholder}}Trivia ==\n* The [[wgg:terraria:Frozen_Banana_Daiquiri|Frozen Banana Daiquiri]] is an item in ''Terraria''.\n** Wilson's quote \"Yellow and mellow!\" is a reference to its tooltip in ''Terraria''.\n*A [[Wikipedia:Daiquiri|Daiquiri]] is a cocktail made from rum, citrus juice (often lime), and a sweetener. Frozen variations, including a banana daiquiri, are also common.\n{{Crock Pot Food}}\n[[vi:Frozen Banana Daiquiri]]"
}
